<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Otto Auer von Au</head><p>Der Rat gewährt dem Adressaten bis Palmtag drei Tage Geleit, um sich in einer Klage zu verantworten.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_279" id="139v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_279_r1l14"><expan>Ott<ex>en</ex></expan> Awer ʒu Awe </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_279_r1l15"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Ott als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt vvıe ewch geſagt ſey . daʒ Jr gen vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l16">verklagt ſüllt ſein / Vnd darauf geleyts ʒu vns begert . eẅch des ʒu ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l17"><expan>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> . etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd wenn Jr <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l18">dem Palmtag ſchıerıſt kombt vnd des begert So <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l19">vns vnd von vns . für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> drey tag geleyt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l20"><expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd eẅr red <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> letare </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_279" id="139v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ott<ex>en</ex></expan> Awer zu Awe </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Ott, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch gesagt sey, daz ir
                        gen uns verklagt süllt sein, und darauf geleyts zu uns begert, ewch des zu
                                ver<expan>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Und wenn ir <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> und dem <app><note><q type="date">palmtag schierist</q>12.04.1416</note></app>
                        kombt und des begert, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewch zu uns und
                        von uns, für uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on
                                <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> drey tag geleyt
                            <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und ewr red <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        hören. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> letare. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
